#ROOM
Vnum     15012
Name     &GThe Chieftain's Tent - Entrance&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Two massive, intricately carved totems flank the entrance to the largest
and most ornate tent in Thunder Bluff. Elite Bloodhoof Braves stand guard
here, ensuring that the High Chieftain is not disturbed without good
reason.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    15011
Desc      The southern walk of the mesa.
~
