  Reset E 1 15001 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     15013
Name     &GThe Chieftain's Tent&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The interior of the tent is surprisingly humble. There is no gilded
throne, only a large, woven mat upon the earth. Maps of Mulgore and
the Barrens are spread across a low wooden table. High Chieftain
Cairne Bloodhoof stands here, exuding a quiet, immense power.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    15012
Desc      The entrance back to the mesa.
~
