#ROOM
Vnum     15014
Name     &GCentral Mesa - West Walk&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The grass here gives way to a sturdy wooden ramp that spirals upward
around a massive central pillar of stone. This is the base of the
Wind Rider Roost, the highest point in all of Thunder Bluff.
~
Exit
Direction east~
ToRoom    15003
Desc      Totem Square.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
