~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     15015
Name     &GThe Wind Rider Roost - Base&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You are ascending a wide wooden ramp that spirals around a towering
stone pinnacle. The wind whips fiercely here, pulling at your clothes.
Above you, you can hear the shrieks of the mighty Wind Riders.
~
Exit
Direction up~
ToRoom    15016
Desc      The ramp continues to the peak.
~
#ENDEXIT
Exit
Direction down~
ToRoom    15014
Desc      The ramp leads down to the mesa.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     15016
Name     &GThe Wind Rider Roost - Peak&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand at the very apex of Thunder Bluff. The view is unparalleled;
you can see for miles across the golden plains of Mulgore. Several
